{"tid":1950654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"24名歐洲議會議員去信林鄭 促撤控黎智英等 獨立調查警暴","createTime":"2020-03-30T12:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T13:18:25.000Z","uid":41404,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"68b30bdb0f417a4a6f4b1e548bd0229f0578b82f","tid":1950654,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英、民主黨前主席楊森及工黨前立法會議員李卓人，因涉嫌參與去年8.31遊行，被控非法集結，案件將於5月於東區法院處理。3人被捕引起國際關注，多名歐洲議會議員聯署去信特首林鄭月娥，指有關拘控行動不成比例及不合理（disproportionate and not justified），促請特區政府撤控，以及成立獨立調查委員會調查警暴及落實普選。<br />\n<br />\n24名歐洲議會議員包括對華關係小組主席Reinhard B&uuml;tikofer等今日去信特首林鄭月娥，關注黎智英、李卓人及楊森被捕一事，信中指3人被控非法集結，但《基本法》賦予香港集會、言論、新聞及出版自由等，強調特別是集會和言論自由十分重要，對於去年8.31和平遊行、表達訴求的人士，作出限制及判刑，均不符比例及不合理。<br />\n<br />\n聯署議員要求特區政府撤銷對黎智英、李卓人及楊森的控罪，並針對警暴問題成立獨立調查委員會，並兌現《基本法》的普選承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/HGJXZRX6VPVIJCVV3FATGFII7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FHGJXZRX6VPVIJCVV3FATGFII7I%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2S%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=28699d3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FHGJXZRX6VPVIJCVV3FATGFII7I%2F&h=b63a3162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/HGJXZRX6VPVIJCVV3FATGFII7I/</a>"},{"pid":"74cb61e163b034c0c06f5abe11d268512fbe7ffd","tid":1950654,"uid":103981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"呢刻佢地仲關心香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21051ddc32ddff85aee435284f0ef85408ac5d9a","tid":1950654,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0fffde0bb40019b44e0462a8212c44a9af699e3b","tid":1950654,"uid":5094,"like":0,"disli